inn1.comm: nudges it out to Hussey
Just outside the off stump. Guptill pushes it back and Bracken fields in his follow through
Fires in a quicker ball, defended to leg side
flicked to backward square leg. Hilfenhaus misfields and the batsmen manage three out of what should have been a dot ball
leaves a lifting ball outside off stump
Slower ball angled across the batsman. Defends on the offside
Shorter ball, defends awkwardly
angled down leg turned off the hip.
Squared up and defended on offside
nudged to mid on
Guptil gets on the back foot and pushes into the covers. Hopes slides across put they're through for a quick single
Guided to backward point, no run there
pushes wide of off stump. No shot offered
pushed wide of off stump again
pushed to point. David Hussey rushes in to field
rocks onto the back foot and drives through the covers. Clarke has to work hard to chase the ball down before the boundary
Drives at the ball and fielded at forward point
Charges and plays backward of pint. flicked to the stumps and they take an overthrow
edged to third man
defended a rising ball into covers
driven to mid on
cross bat smash to point
attempts to flick it down to backward square leg but can't get the ball away
Turned off the but this time fielded cleanly at backward square leg
On the front foot, pushed into the covers where Mike Hussey fields
Leaves one outside off stump angled across him
Full delivery and drives. Bracken jumps high to field in his follow through
Pitched up and square drives. Ponting does well to cut it off and fires it back at Haddin who does some acrobatics with the return
Gets forward and defends
On the backfoot and angled to Ponting at point
Backfoot defence to extra cover where Hopes fields well
Short of a length and played just forward of point where Ponting fields
Pitched up, Pushed to Clarke at mid off
Pitched on middle and leg and played through mid wicket
On the backfoot and played in the air to backward point. Falls short of Ponting
Backfoot and steers it wide of Ponting at point
A slower ball, onto the front foot and played to Mike Hussey at mid wicket
Gets back and attempts to steer to third man, risky shot
gets forward and drops the ball at his feet and runs. Memories of Dean Jones there
left outside off stump
played to point
wide, down leg side
pushed to mid wicket for a single
angled down leg side and just gets an edge to it down to backward square leg
forward and drives through point
wide outside off stump and McCullum smashes the ball straight to Ponting at point. That flew off the bat
Drives on the up, but straight to Hussey in the covers, just can't get it through the field
Over the wicket and the batsman is on the front foot and defending
Bracken charges in and its defended on the offside
Strays on to leg stump and flicked off the pads to backward square leg. 12th man Voges fields in the deep
Over the wicket and Guptil defends on onside
Drives in the air, falls short of the mid off fieldsman
Opens the shoulders and its gone miles over long on
McCullum drives into covers. Clarke does the fielding
Forward and defends to Hussey at short cover
guided to third man. Hilfenhaus fields
shorter ball defended down. Johnson fields
Defends into covers. Hussey fields again
Puched through the covers. Hopes chases, pauses and throws but they are home
on line with the stump, giving no freedom whatsoever to McCullum to free his arms. He just manages to defend it on the off side
good length delivery outside the off stump. McCullum runs the ball down to third man for a single
short outside the off stump. Guptill, can't clear the field on the off side as he cuts it straight to the point fielder
fuller outside the off stump, Guptill comes forward and presents the full face of the bat
good length delivery outside the off stump, Guptill gets his bat down in an arc but can't manage to beat the fielder positioned at short cover
fuller on the leg stump, cramps Guptill up for room. Guptill, just manages to squeeze it to midwicket
outside the off stump, McCullum gets onto the backfoot and defends
short outside the off stump, McCullum gets onto the backfoot and allows the ball to come onto the bat as he steals a single

short on the middle stump, almost rushing onto Guptill as he looks to pull it away but does not manage to get any bat on it as the ball hits the helmet on it's way to the boundary. A Mistake there as they are awarded as runs
outside the off stump, Guptill flashes his bat at it and is beaten
outside the off stump again. This time Guptill decides to play it closer to the body as he attempts to run it down to third man but the late swing beats him again
good length delivery outside the off stump to begin with as McCullum shuffles across and works it to midwicket
short outside the off stump as he sees McCullum come charging down the track. McCullum pushes it to point and sets off for a single
outside the off stump yet again as Guptill presents the full face of the bat in defense
on the leg stump, Guptill works it away to long leg for a couple
outside the off stump, Guptill comes forward and defends
fuller outside the off stump. Guptill drives but can't clear trhe fielder at short cover again
outside the off stump, McCullum opens the face of the bat and runs the ball to cover for a single
outside the off stump, Guptill defends convincingly yet again but that is not what he should be doing
outside the off stump, Guptill opens the face of the bat to run  the ball down to point
finally Guptill manages to find the gap on the off side as he thrashes an over-pitched delivery to cover boundary. Thats his first boundary on the off-side
wide outside the off stump
good length delivery outside the off stump. Guptill drives but gets a thick outside edge to third man for a single
fuller outside the off stump. Guptill, comes onto the frontfoot and drives it to mid-off
outside the off stump, Guptill pushes it to mid-on and runs across for a single
on the middle stump and cutting in. McCullum closes the face of the bat and pushes it to midwicket for a single. He brings up the fifty with that single
outside the off stump, McCullum pushes it to point
good length delivery outside the off stump. McCullum comes charging down the track and changes his mind at the last moment as he pushes it to point
good length delivery outside the off stump, Guptill, gets a thick outside edge to the right of third man for a couple
short on the leg stump. Guptill, stands tall and plays it down with soft hands on the leg side for a single
short on the leg stump, McCullum looks to pull it away but is struck on the pads as he runs across for a leg-bye
fuller outside the off stump, Guptill, gets under the delivery easily as he chips it over mid-off for a boundary
short length delivery outside the off stump, Guptill plays it to cover off the backfoot
short on the off and middle. Guptill, gets onto the backfoot and plays it to the vacant area on the leg side to pick a single
fuller outside the off stump to begin with. Guptill  pushes it back to the bowler
on the middle stump, Guptill pushes it to midwicket
arm ball on the middle stump, Guptill, plays it with soft hands back to the bowler
arm ball again. Guptill is struck on the pads this time around
short on the middle stump, Guptill pushes it to long-on for a single
fuller and faster on the middle stump, McCulum stands tall and pushes it back to the bowler
outside the off stump. Guptill, runs it down to third man for a couple
short and wide outside the off stump, Guptill cuts it but gets a top edge that flies over the point fielder for a boundary
outside the off stump, pushes it to point for a single
good length delivery on the middle stump, McCullum jumps around in the crease and pushes it to square leg for a single

gone! Johnson pitches one short on the middle and leg stump this time around and hurries Guptill into the stroke. He manages to get some wood on the ball as he pulls it straight into the hands of Bracken, positioned at fine-leg exactly for this
outside the off stump, Fulton moves across and defends it to the leg side
good lenght delivery on the off stump. McCullum looks to defend it but gets an inside edge to square leg
comes down the track and defends
outside the off stump, McCullum comes down the track and defends it
short outside the off stump, McCullum cuts it late to deep point for a couple
fuller delivery on the middle stump, McCullum comes down the track and defends it again
on the leg stump, McCullum turns it to fine leg for a single
outside the off stump, McCullum comes forward and defends it back to the bowler
outside the off stump and fuller too as McCullum beats Clarke at mid-off to fetch three runs for himself
fuller outside the off stump, Fulton drives it wide off the bowler to long-on for a couple
outside the off stump, Fulton comes forward and pushes it to the off side
good length delivery on the middle stump, Fulton turns it to midwicket for a single
outside the off stump, McCullum tries to run it down but cant clear the fielder at short third man
outside the off stump, Fulton comes forward and pushes it to mid-off for a single
outside the off stump, McCullum pushes it to the off side
on the leg stump, McCullum sweeps it away to fine leg for a single
on the middle stump and an arm ball as Fulton adjusts late and defends it back onto the pitch
arm ball on the middle stump, Fulton drives it to cover for a single
drives it to cover for another single
good length delivery on the pads as McCullum turns it to fine-leg for a single
good length delivery outside the off stump, Fulton defends it to cover
fuller on the off stump, Fulton, looks to work it away on the leg side but gets an outside edge to short third man
one more! Fulton falls now as he does not manage to keep the ball down as he plays an intended drive on the off side to Bracken at mid-on and Kiwis slip further now
fuller on the middle stump, McCullum pushes it to midwicket for a single
on the leg stump, Taylor pushes it to the short cover fielder
fuller length delivery on the middle stump, McCullum drives it back to the bowler
on the leg stump, McCullum moves across and sweeps it to short fine leg for a single
outside the off stump, Taylor comes forward and defends it to cover
on the leg stump, Taylor pushes it to long-on for a single
outside the off stump, McCullum drives it to mid-off

timber! McCullum is beaten by the arm ball on the run. He comes down the track in an attempt to loft it away but is beaten by the arm ball pitching on the middle stump and finds his leg stump displaced. This is even more bad news as two wickets fall in two overs
on the middle and off stump line, Taylor pushes forward and defends it away towards cover
similar line and length and Taylor is happy presenting the full face of the bat and watching the ball roll away silently
bit fuller but once again the line is good, Taylor, give the situation, I guess,  taps it away on the off side
placed wide of the fielder at cover, easy single
another harmless delivery, watchfully defended
punched off the back-foot to the point region
drifting onto middle and leg, Taylor waits for the ball to turn and then works it away well in front of square leg for a single
quicker delivery outside the off stump, driven straight to the man at cover
angled in from outside the off stump, defended down on the leg side
worked away off the back-foot
slightly short, Elliott stays back and punches it away wide of the fielder at cover
another easy single on the off side
good length delivery outside the off stump, Taylor lines it up but the drive finds the fielder at mid-off
surprise bouncer and it nearly did the trick. Taylor goes for the pull instinctively and the ball balloons up towards backward square. Hussey runs in towards his left but fails it get there on time
worked away on the leg side for an easy single
Hopes keeps it tight outside the off stump, defended
fuller length delivery and that's driven straight to Ponting at short cover
good length delivery outside the off stump, Taylor runs it away behind point but fails to get it past the fielder. Another good over from Hopes comes to an end
starts off with a skidder and that is played away towards midwicket
goes for the drive but not a well timed shot and the ball rolls away off the inner half of the bat
driven off the front-foot, straight to the fielder at cover
driven square on the off side, just enough room and they scamper through for a single
short and angling in, Taylor rocks back and cuts it past the fielder at point
on the middle and off stump line, punched straight back to the fielder
good length outside the off stump, Elliot shuffles across and runs it down to third man for a single
outside the off stump, Taylor tries to run it down to third man but gets an inside edge back onto the pitch
outside the off stump, drives it back to the bowler
outside the off stump, Taylor looks to slog it away on the leg side but gets a leading edge to cover
short outside the off stump and Elliot cuts it to deep point for a couple
fuller on the leg and middle, Taylor comes down the track and pushes it to long-on for a single and it brings the hundred up
good length delivery on the off stump, Elliot stands tall and drives it to sweeper cover for a single
fuller on the off stump, Taylor pushes it to the leg side
fuller outside the off stump, Taylor pushes it to sweeper cover for a single
outside the off stump, Elliot square drives it to deep point for a single
outside the off stump, Taylor pushes it to the right of the point fielder for a single
begins with a good leg break outside the off stump. Taylor watches it right into the gloves of Haddin
outside the off stump, Taylor comes forward and defends it
a googly gone terribly wrong as he flights it a lot more and Taylor picks it as he knocks the leather out of the ball in sending it soaring over fine leg for a six
outside the off stump, Taylor comes forward and pushes it back to the bowler
short outside the off stump, Taylor, cuts it to deep point for a single
fuller on the leg stump. Invitation for Elliot to sweep and sweep he does for a single
short outside the off stump, Elliot looks to cut it away and is beaten
and pushes it to covers for a single
good length delivery on the off stump. Taylor drives it back to the bowler
outside the off stump, Taylor drives it back to the bowler
on the middle stump, Taylor drives it to short mid-on, where Ponting is doing the duties
short outside the off stump, Taylor cuts it to point for a single
fuller on the off stump, Taylor drives it to long-on for a single
fuller outside the off stump, Elliot smashes it to cover for a boundary
drives it to sweeper cover for a couple
now he lets loose a slog sweep as he propels it to midwicket for a boundary
on the leg stump, Elliot pushes it to midwicket for a single

outside the off stump, Taylor cuts it past the point fielder and Hussey, drags it back in but not before he touches the ropes and Taylor too helps himself to a boundary. White was taken to task there as he conceded 16 runs off the over
good length delivery outside the off stump, Elliot drives it wide of the long-off fielder for a couple
outside the off stump, Elliot runs it down to third man for a single
short outside the off stump, Taylor slog sweeps it to midwicket for a boundary and now they are revving it up
inside edge to deep square leg for a single
cut to point
outside the off stump, comes forward and defends it to midwicket
outside the off stump, Taylor comes forward and drives it to midwicket
outside the off stump, Taylor, is looking to drive it away on the off side but is beaten by the delivery cutting away
fuller delivery on the middle stump. Taylor, drives it to mid-on for a single
short and wide outside the off stump. Elliot, moves across and cuts it to the left of Hilfenhaus to fetch himself a couple
Elliot shuffles across before the ball is bowled and Johnson notices it as he pitches it short on the middle and leg. Elliot lets it go

short on the middle stump. Elliot does the pre-meditated shuffle and swats it in the gap between fine-leg and sweeper on the leg side. David Hussey, covers a lot of ground as he takes a good catch. It was more of a good catch from Hussey than a poor shot from Elliot
outside the off stump, comes forward and defends it to point
defends it to cover point yet again
short ball outside the off stump, Cumming gets an outside edge to cover
good length outside the off stump, Cumming comes forward and drives it back to the bowler
short outside the off stump, Cumming sways out of the harm's way pretty easily

gone! Cumming just manages to chip it to mid-off, where Johnson takes a straight-forward catch. It means Cumming has fluffed his chances in his first ODI in four years. Australia are in the driver's seat now
drives it to mid-off
looks to defend it on the frontfoot and gets an outside edge to third man for a single
outside the off stump, Broom comes forward and pushes it to short mid-off
outside the off stump. Broom shoulders arms to the delivery
good length delivery on the middle stump. Broom comes forward and closes the face of the bat as he pushes it to midwicket
on the middle stump, Broom, stands tall and pushes it to the leg side
fuller outside the off stump. Taylor drives it over a leaping Hopes for a single
good length delivery on the middle stump. Broom comes forward and pushes it to midwicket
outside the off stump and short in length. Broom, gets onto the backfoot and pushes it to point
fuller in length on the middle stump. Broom, works it away to midwicket to get off the mark
good length delivery outside the off stump, Taylor plays it with soft hands to point and runs across for a single
short outside the off stump. Broom looks to get the upper cut going but the bounce defeats the purpose
outside the off stump, Taylor looks to play it with soft hands but the ball rushes into him as he defends it back onto the pitch

short outside the off stump, Taylor cuts it to point, where Ponting does the fielding and throws the stumps down at the bowlers end. He ends up conceding a single as the ball is deflected off the stumps
looks to run it down to third man but first slip does the fielding
high above the batsman's head and it is called a wide
full on the middle stump, Taylor works it away to deep midwicket and runs quickly for a couple
overpitches on the leg stump.Taylor, turns it away to fine-leg for a single
and begins with a wide delivery outside the off stump. He laughs it off but bet Ponting wont see the funnier side in it
slower delivery outside the off stump, Taylor pushes it to long-off for a single

outside the off stump and a touch faster as Broom is beaten by the pace as he bottom edges a defensive push and runs across but not before Ponting comes running in and throws the stumps down at the bowler's end
outside the off stump, Broom looks to run it down to third man but gets an outside edge. Haddin, dives across and takes the ball brilliantly and top it off he does a backhand flick too
pushes it to point
short outside the off stump.Broom cuts it to deep point for a single
short outside the off stump. Broom, stands tall and looks to pull it away - his first attacking stroke- and is beaten
good length delivery on the middle stump. Broom pushes it on the leg side and runs across for a single
fuller on the middle stump. Taylor, comes forward and gets his bat down in time to defend the ball back onto the pitch
fuller on the off stump, Taylor, drives it back to the bowler
short on the middle stump. Taylor, spots it early and lets go of the pull shot and clears the deep square leg fielder easily as he sends the ball five rows into the crowd
fuller on the middle stump. Taylor, pushes it back to the bowler
outside the off stump, Broom pushes it to cover and runs across for a quick single
good length delivery outside the off stump. Taylor, drives but does not time it as he runs across for a single
on the middle stump, Broom pushes it to midwicket
outside the off stump. Broom looks to play it with soft hands but is unable to as the ball goes to cover
outside the off stump and on a good length. Broom drives it to long-off for a single
good length delivery outside the off stump. Taylor walks across and drives it to the right of sweeper cover for a couple
on the middle stump. Broom moves across and pushes it to midwicket
outside the off stump and left alone
short and wide down the leg side and rightly called so
fuller on the middle stump. Broom, brings the bat down to jam the ball down as he gets a thick inside edge to the fine-leg boundary

it's all over for Broom. Hilfenhaus, pitches it short and Broom, spontaneously goes for the pull and ends up top edging it to Hopes, stationed at cover. Just when it looked like a partnership was coming on, a wicket falls
and has to face the chin music first up
fuller length delivery on the middle stump. Mills defends it off the backfoot
on the leg stump. Taylor turns it away to fine-leg for a single
outside the off stump and coming in. Mills defends it of the backfoot
outside the off stump. Mills runs it down to third man for a single

! Taylor looks to work it away on the leg side but is early into the shot as he gets a leading edge to a diving Ponting, who gets his left hand to the ball but can't take the catch. Taylor gets a single and moves on to his half-century
outside the off stump, Mills defends it back onto the pitch
a repeat of the defensive stroke from the last ball
short outside the off stump. Hilfenhaus, sledge-hammers it to sweeper cover for a boundary
on the leg stump. Taylor works it away on the leg side for a single
outside the off stump, Mills, comes forward and defends it
short outside the off stump. Mills looks to cut it away but draws his bat back in and lets it pass
short on the middle stump. Mills, this time ducks under it
fuller outside the off stump, Mills, pushes it to mid-off and sets off for a quick single
and Mills enjoys the freedom as he cuts it away to third man for a couple
short on the middle stump. Mills, hops around and defends it back onto the pitch
good length delivery outside the off stump. Mills, looks to heave it away to long-on but is quick into the shot as he is beaten
fuller outside the off stump. Only good fielding by Clarke at mid-off denies Mills a boundary as he has to be happy with a single for now
fuller outside the off stump. Taylor, lets go off the drive and sees David Hussey, bring off a full-length dive to stop a boundary
short delivery on the middle stump and forces Mills into the pull stroke. The top-edged pull just falls short of a diving Hilfenhaus and they run across for a couple
wide outside the off stump to begin the over
fuller outside the off stump. Taylor drives it extra-cover, who is standing on the edge of the circle
this time Taylor splits the gap between cover and extra-cover as he helps himself for a boundary
now he goes inside-out and lofts it over the infield for another boundary
fuller on the leg stump. Taylor, beats the short fine-leg fielder- Bracken - and gets three runs for his efforts
short on the middle stump. Mills moves away and lets go with a cut shot. A boundary is the result
Mills looks to repeat the dose but moves away a little bit more this time. Hilfenhaus follows him and beats the attempted cut shot
fuller outside the off stump. Taylor, comes down the track and chips it to the left of the fielder at long-off for a couple
outside the off stump and cutting away. Taylor, is looking to go for the slog-sweep but the ball cutting away beats the purpose
fuller outside the off stump, Taylor leans across and flat-bats it to midwicket for a couple
full-toss outside the off stump. Taylor, moves across and slogs it to cow corner for a boundary
wide, far too wide outside the off stump. And what adds to Bracken's misery is the fine-leg fielder being inside the circle . He ends up conceding five wides
on the leg stump. Bracken turns it away to fine-leg for a single
on the leg stump, Mills pushes it to midwicket for a single
good length delivery outside the off stump. Mills is looking to go downtown but is beaten by the away movement
on the leg stump. Mills is moving away once again and Johnson follows him as Mills pushes it back to the bowler
up, up and away! Mills backs away to the short delivery and it had six written all over it from the moment it left the bat. The ball is sent onto the roof-top at fine-leg
on the leg stump, Mills looks to work it away but is struck on the pads. Nevertheless, he runs across for a leg-bye

gone! Full-toss on the off stump. Taylor, moves across and looks to get cheeky as he wants to paddle it to fine-leg but the ball comes in faster than he expects. Taylor, manages to get a top edge which flies high. Haddin is calling for it right from the moment it flew and takes the catch
slower delivery outside the off stump. Mills pushes it to mid-off for a quick single
fuller on the off stump. Mills moves away and drives it to long-off for a couple
on the leg stump, Mills pushes it to midwicket for a single
short on the leg stump. Vettori, the new batsman pulls it to square leg for a single
fuller on the middle stump. Mills, chips it to deep midwicket for a single
full-toss angled onto the pads. Vettori, guides it to deep square leg for three runs

timber! Mills is backing away even before the ball is bowled. Bracken notices it and bowls a yorker on the middle stump. Mills has a swing and there is only place where the ball can go- stumps- if he misses and it does go there
drifts onto the pads as Vettori pushes it to midwicket for a single
full-toss on the middle stump. Southee, moves across and slogs it to deep midwicket for a single
outside the off stump, Vettori guides it to third man for a single
yorker on the off stump. Southee jams it to long-on and runs across for a quick couple
yorker on the middle stump, Southee pushes it to deep square leg for a couple
fuller on the leg stump. Southee, comes down the track and plays it to deep midwicket and takes the couple

inn2.comm: Mills bowls a fuller delivery and Haddin looks to work it away on the leg side. Haddin gets a leading edge and gets the scorecard moving
outside the off stump, Clarke, gets to the pitch of the delivery and drives it to sweeper cover for a couple
fuller on the middle stump, Clarke, works it away to deep square leg for a single
bowls on the pads once again as Haddin works it away to deep square leg for a single
good length delivery outside the off stump. Clarke, gets his foot to the pitch of the delivery and lets it pass to the keeper
outside the off stump. Clarke, once again gets to the pitch of the delivery and shoulders arms
outside the off stump and Haddin is not interested
good length delivery outside the off stump. Haddin, moves across and pushes the delivery to cover
wide down the leg side
good length delivery outside the off stump, devoid of any movement. Haddin gets behind the line of the delivery and lets it pass to the keeper
thats the Haddin we got to know from Sydney as he moves away a touch and smashes a short length delivery in the gap between cover and point for a boundary
outside the off stump. Haddin, gets solidly behind the line of the delivery and defends it
fuller on the off stump. Haddin, does not connect with the intended drive as it just falls short of Elliot at mid-on
good length delivery on the off stump. Clarke, leans across and pushes it to mid-on
short outside the off stump. Clarke, stands tall and pushes it to cover
short outside the off stump. Clarke, is looking to play it with soft hands but gets an inside edge back onto the pitch
good length delivery outside the off stump, Clarke drives it to mid-off
fuller length delivery outside the off stump. Clarke, drives but good fielding by Fulton at short cover prevents not only a boundary but a run too
full delivery on the off stump, Clarke, drives it to the right of mid-off fielder for a single
sheer timing there as Southee, bowls a full delivery outside the off stump. Clarke drives it past Southee, who does well to get some hand onto it and prevents an extra run
good length delivery outside the off stump. Haddin, gets behind the line of the delivery and defends
outside the off stump and short in length. Haddin looks to cut it away and gets a bottom edge back to the keeper
rank bad ball as Haddin gets behind the short delivery easily and pulls it away to deep square-leg for a boundary
good length delivery outside the off stump. Haddin, comes forward and pushes it to cover
bad bowling again by Southee as he pitches it short and Haddin, is happy to pull it away to deep square leg for another boundary
fuller on the off stump. Clarke, does amazingly well to move his frontfoot across and chips it over the infield on the leg-side for a boundary. Top shot that
short outside the off stump. Clarke, drives it to cover off the backfoot
short outside the off stump, Clarke, is putting the cover fielder under severe test as he cuts it to him and the fielder does pass the test
off the inside edge onto the pads as they run across for a single
outside the off stump and short in length. Haddin, gets behind the line of the delivery and defends it
outside the off stump. Haddin, comes forward and drives it to mid-off
and immediately has a sniff at wicket as he manages to entice Clarke into playing a drive which just manages to beat the outstretched fingers of Elliot at mid-on
defends on the frontfoot
outside the off stump, defends on the backfoot

and the bowling change works! O'Brein bowls one on the off stump. Clarke, drives it on the up and ends up spooning an easy catch to Fulton at short cover. Fulton, has been an exceptional fielder close-in
outside the off stump, Ponting, comes forward and pushes it back to the bowler
on the pads. Ponting, looks to work it away and is rapped on the pads
outside the off stump and on a good length. Haddin, gets behind the line of the delivery and defends it
fuller in length outside the off stump. Haddin, comes forward and drives it to mid-off
good length delivery on the middle stump. Haddin, pushes it to the leg-side off the backfoot
good length delivery outside the off stump. Haddin treats it with utmost respect as he defends on the frontfoot
outside the off stump, Haddin, gets behind the line of the delivery and defends it
outside the off stump, Haddin, pushes it to point
bowls it full and straight on the off stump, he;s running in hard, Ponting gets forward and pushes it to mid-off
just opens the face of the bat and steers this one wide of gully
just holds the length back a bit, he gets across on the backfoot and defends
sticks to the same line and length and he defends solidly on the backfoot again
this time he defends with an angled bat and steers it down the vacant backward point region
good length delivery on the middle and off stump line, Haddin makes room and looks to go inside-out through extra cover but the shot is not timed well enough and the ball rolls down to mid-on
punched away on the off side
quicker delivery, Haddin goes hard at it and the ball races away to third man, more edge than middle

that's plumb but not given. Good length delivery, pitched outside the off stump and this one jagged back in. Ponting pushes forward to drive and is beaten by the angle. Looked out but umpire Davis was not impressed.
wide outside the off stump and Ponting is beaten on the drive
this one came back in but is wide outside the off stump
line and length delivery outside the off stump, worked away towards cover
take that! short and wide outside the off stump, Haddin quickly gets into position and slams it past the fielder at point
four more. This one is pitched up and O'Brien finds out why that is not the length to bowl. Haddin gets right behind the line and hammers it straight back down the ground long-on fence
follows it up with a good yorker and Haddin defends it watchfully
pushed away on the off side, no room for a single there
good length delivery and this one kept bit low. Haddin reads it well and taps it away on the off side
short and wide outside the off stump, cut straight to the fielder at point. Missed out there on an easy boundary
